rows.label: qst620501_msg0001
rows.name: Guys! GUYS!

rows.label: qst620501_msg0002
rows.name:
Wake up, wake up! We gotta
get outta here, now now now!

rows.label: qst620501_msg0003
rows.name:
Even Ibuki couldn't be THIS
worked up over nothing... Right?

rows.label: qst620501_msg0004
rows.name: Very well put...

rows.label: qst620501_msg0005
rows.name:
Whoa, whoa, Ibuki! Slow down!
What's brought all this on?

rows.label: qst620501_msg0006
rows.name:
Just now, right, I was walkin'
'round when I hear the most
awful news! They said that-

rows.label: qst620501_msg0007
rows.name:
...They said!
They said...

rows.label: qst620501_msg0008
rows.name: It was...

rows.label: qst620501_msg0009
rows.name: Um...

rows.label: qst108301_msg0016
rows.name: 鳥頭　LV.3

rows.label: qst620501_msg0010
rows.name: I forgot.

rows.label: qst620501_msg0011
rows.name: Saw that one coming.

rows.label: qst620501_msg0012
rows.name:
It must have been really big,
right? Can you remember
anything at all?

rows.label: qst620501_msg0013
rows.name: Nope, too late! It's gone now.

rows.label: qst620501_msg0014
rows.name: I'm tryin' but nothin's comin' back!

rows.label: qst620501_msg0015
rows.name:
But I remember it was something
about Marge! I definitely maybe heard
her name.

rows.label: qst620501_msg0016
rows.name:
Meleph. My name is Meleph. 
How many times do we have
to go over this?

rows.label: qst620501_msg0017
rows.name:
Huh? Really? Weird.
Are you sure?

rows.label: qst620501_msg0018
rows.name:
...Very sure.
In any case, I'm curious to know
more about what's going on.

rows.label: qst620501_msg0019
rows.name:
I'm jolly well intrigued too.
We should investigate.

rows.label: qst620501_msg0020
rows.name:
Hmm, how about we put a few
mercs on it, then?

rows.label: qst620501_msg0021
rows.name: You guys! Thanks so much!

rows.label: qst620501_msg0022
rows.name: I hope we can work it out somehow...
